results.title: Life Should Not Be Measured By the Number of Years Sign
results.description:
Life should not be measured by the number of years but by the love shared, the memories made, the joy given and the blessings received. This rustic sign is distressed and antiqued to give a prim look and makes a wonderful gift for just about anyone. 

This handpainted sign is made to order. Shipment is generally 3 to 5 business days. Signs shown are Black and Antique White and Brown and Antique White. 

Each sign measures approximately 12 inches by 16 inches. For this sign we use blondewood, approx. 3/8 inch thick.  Our handcrafted creations are made using a 7 step process which creates a beautiful expression to be cherished for years to come. Two contrasting colors of paint are applied first. Then the saying is applied to the sign with a fine hairline added on all of the lettering which gives an awesome touch. After those steps are completed the sign is cleaned and goes through our antiquing process with edges distressed, giving it the final touches. Ready to Hang with hanger attached on the back side. 

There are various color choices to choose from but if you don't see what you are looking for, please let us know and we will see if we can make it happen for you. Keep in mind when selecting the color options listed, the first color is the base color, while the second color is the top coat. The most popular color for our signs is Black and Antique White by far. The second most popular color is Brown and Antique White. 

Please let us know what color you want in the note section when ordering. If no color is specified we will make the sign using Black and Antique White.

COLOR CHOICES INCLUDE
Black/Antique White
Black/Country Tan
Black/Light Pink
Black/Sunflower
Barn Red/Antique White
Barn Red/Country Tan
Burgundy/Antique White
Burgundy/Country Tan
Brown/Antique White
Brown/Light Pink
Brown/Hot Pink
Brown/Sunflower
Brown/Sky Blue
Purple/Antique White
Hunter Green/Antique White
JohnDeere Green/Sunflower
Midnite Blue/Antique White 


Please note these signs are not massed produced but each is unique and no two are exactly the same. When working with wood and the antiquing process, each sign has its own warmth and charm.

results.title: Long Silk Scarf Blue, Live Love Laugh, Wishes, Infinity scarf Handpainted, Long Scarf 8x71 inches,  Birthday Gift, Ready to ship.
results.description:
'Live, Love, Laugh' - long silk scarf features handwritten wishes on a bright background in blue hues. This scarf is a part of my new 'Best Wishes' scarf series.
Long enough to wrap it around your neck and wear it like an infinity scarf or tie it in so many different ways! Perfect gift!

• Size: 8" x 71" (20cm x 180cm)
• Materials: 100% Habotai silk. Professional silk dyes.
• Care: Hand wash, iron on silk setting. Care instruction card is included with purchase.
• Comes gift wrapped.

I created this scarf using a special method which is called the SERTI technique, when design is applied with resist that keeps dyes within the outlined areas. After the dye has dried, the silk is steam set for 4 hours. This increases the brilliance of the color and allows the dye to permanently bond to the silk on a molecular level. After that, the silk is colorfast and washable.

I hand paint each scarf with much devotion and care. My scarves are not mass produced items. I sign all my work so you know they are original hand painted just for you.

This scarf is AVAILABLE for purchase and READY TO SHIP.
